1
00:00:59,480 --> 00:01:00,740
Xiaocen, you're here.

2
00:01:01,200 --> 00:01:03,120
I heard you were sick a few days ago.

3
00:01:03,120 --> 00:01:04,650
Are you feeling better now?

4
00:01:04,920 --> 00:01:05,650
Much better.

5
00:01:07,160 --> 00:01:08,480
These past few days you weren't here,

6
00:01:08,480 --> 00:01:10,480
I felt Xu Xiao wasn't in a good state.

7
00:01:10,760 --> 00:01:12,620
He seemed very worried about you.

8
00:01:21,160 --> 00:01:22,020
Xu Xiao is here.

9
00:01:22,360 --> 00:01:23,220
Xu Xiao is here.

10
00:01:31,200 --> 00:01:31,720
Are you

11
00:01:33,160 --> 00:01:34,090
feeling better?

12
00:01:35,240 --> 00:01:35,970
I'm fine now.

13
00:01:38,560 --> 00:01:40,890
My mom didn't say anything to you, did she?

14
00:01:43,000 --> 00:01:43,800
Nothing much.

15
00:01:49,400 --> 00:01:49,930
Morning.

16
00:01:58,680 --> 00:01:59,810
Are you alright now?

17
00:02:01,200 --> 00:02:02,060
Class monitor,

18
00:02:02,240 --> 00:02:03,640
is everyone here?

19
00:02:04,040 --> 00:02:04,960
Everyone's here.

20
00:02:04,960 --> 00:02:05,480
Class,

21
00:02:06,200 --> 00:02:08,039
Today is the last class of Introduction to Cultural Relics Studies

22
00:02:08,039 --> 00:02:09,560
for this semester.

23
00:02:10,120 --> 00:02:11,180
Time really flies.

24
00:02:11,600 --> 00:02:13,360
The semester has gone by in a flash.

25
00:02:13,360 --> 00:02:14,880
I wonder if you still remember

26
00:02:14,880 --> 00:02:17,120
how you felt when you first walked into this classroom

27
00:02:17,120 --> 00:02:18,720
and sat in these seats.

28
00:02:23,520 --> 00:02:24,120
Xiaocen.

29
00:02:24,400 --> 00:02:25,160
Mr. Yue.

30
00:02:25,920 --> 00:02:26,520
Xiaocen,

31
00:02:28,240 --> 00:02:29,500
where's your partner?

32
00:02:31,320 --> 00:02:32,450
Probably behind me.

33
00:02:43,079 --> 00:02:43,800
Hurry up.

34
00:02:44,360 --> 00:02:44,960
What's wrong?

35
00:02:44,960 --> 00:02:46,400
Did you hear

36
00:02:46,640 --> 00:02:48,120
about your little partner?

37
00:02:48,120 --> 00:02:48,800
Hear what?

38
00:02:50,400 --> 00:02:52,520
Her mother called the department

39
00:02:52,520 --> 00:02:54,200
asking about changing her major.

40
00:02:54,200 --> 00:02:55,000
I didn't know.

41
00:02:57,079 --> 00:02:59,140
What are you waiting for? Go quickly.

42
00:03:02,520 --> 00:03:03,480
These parents

43
00:03:04,200 --> 00:03:06,360
are more troublesome than the students.

44
00:03:06,360 --> 00:03:07,160
Zhao Xiaocen!

45
00:03:07,320 --> 00:03:08,120
Zhao Xiaocen!

46
00:03:14,320 --> 00:03:15,980
You want to change your major.

47
00:03:17,120 --> 00:03:17,800
I'm sorry.

48
00:03:19,120 --> 00:03:19,520
I

49
00:03:20,040 --> 00:03:21,640
didn't know how to tell you.

50
00:03:21,840 --> 00:03:23,040
I've told you before.

51
00:03:23,600 --> 00:03:24,400
In this world,

52
00:03:24,400 --> 00:03:26,860
I'm the last person you need to apologize to.

53
00:03:30,480 --> 00:03:31,740
I just want to tell you,

54
00:03:33,920 --> 00:03:36,050
you need to think more about yourself.

55
00:03:37,040 --> 00:03:38,300
Follow your own heart.

56
00:03:40,760 --> 00:03:42,220
No matter what you choose,

57
00:03:44,079 --> 00:03:44,880
I will respect

58
00:03:46,720 --> 00:03:47,650
and support you.

59
00:04:10,360 --> 00:04:11,840
Your dad and I have discussed it.

60
00:04:11,840 --> 00:04:12,560
We're changing your major.

61
00:04:12,560 --> 00:04:13,960
We've made the decision.

62
00:04:14,000 --> 00:04:15,960
Then what exactly are you discussing with me?

63
00:04:15,960 --> 00:04:16,920
I am your mother.

64
00:04:17,320 --> 00:04:18,839
You have to do as I say.

65
00:04:21,079 --> 00:04:23,410
Haven't you ever thought about going out?

66
00:04:24,000 --> 00:04:24,600
Of course.

67
00:04:25,400 --> 00:04:26,320
I've always wanted to go

68
00:04:26,320 --> 00:04:27,920
to the place where you grew up

69
00:04:28,160 --> 00:04:29,020
and take a look.

70
00:04:38,920 --> 00:04:40,000
I want to be like you

71
00:04:41,400 --> 00:04:42,600
and be brave for once.

72
00:04:44,520 --> 00:04:45,080
Xiaocen.

73
00:04:48,240 --> 00:04:48,920
I like you.

74
00:05:39,880 --> 00:05:43,080
Don't keep looking at me like that, okay?

75
00:05:43,360 --> 00:05:45,200
It's like I'm about to die.

76
00:05:46,200 --> 00:05:48,200
I'm just worried about you, Master.

77
00:05:50,760 --> 00:05:51,920
How is the kiln?

78
00:05:52,720 --> 00:05:54,120
The fire is out and it's cooling.

79
00:05:54,120 --> 00:05:55,250
Everything is fine.

80
00:05:56,120 --> 00:05:56,680
Good.

81
00:05:58,360 --> 00:06:00,400
Crank it up a bit for me.

82
00:06:05,880 --> 00:06:07,080
Is this okay, Master?

83
00:06:07,080 --> 00:06:07,810
A bit higher.

84
00:06:09,360 --> 00:06:10,120
Good, good.

85
00:06:13,160 --> 00:06:14,120
Guan Lin.

86
00:06:17,200 --> 00:06:18,080
You know,

87
00:06:18,560 --> 00:06:20,520
when firing a wood kiln,

88
00:06:21,600 --> 00:06:23,330
there are eight leg positions.

89
00:06:23,560 --> 00:06:24,840
Eight levels.

90
00:06:25,560 --> 00:06:26,920
The top three are

91
00:06:28,600 --> 00:06:31,040
top stacker,

92
00:06:31,880 --> 00:06:33,240
kiln planner,

93
00:06:34,080 --> 00:06:35,200
and chief kiln.

94
00:06:37,760 --> 00:06:39,360
The bottom three are...

95
00:06:39,440 --> 00:06:40,080
I know.

96
00:06:41,120 --> 00:06:43,440
Don't interrupt. Let me finish.

97
00:06:44,800 --> 00:06:46,440
The bottom three are

98
00:06:47,000 --> 00:06:50,600
First Apprentice, Second Apprentice, and Third Apprentice.

99
00:06:51,480 --> 00:06:52,280
In the middle,

100
00:06:52,600 --> 00:06:53,159
there are

101
00:06:53,520 --> 00:06:56,240
young potter and bottom stacker.

102
00:06:57,800 --> 00:07:01,840
I started from the lowest level, First Apprentice.

103
00:07:02,960 --> 00:07:04,480
Every day,

104
00:07:05,560 --> 00:07:08,680
I spent 16 or 17 hours in the kiln.

105
00:07:10,120 --> 00:07:11,480
Every three days,

106
00:07:11,840 --> 00:07:13,100
we fired the kiln once.

107
00:07:14,360 --> 00:07:15,720
So every year,

108
00:07:18,440 --> 00:07:21,160
I had to practice in front of the kiln

109
00:07:21,920 --> 00:07:24,280
more than a hundred times a year.

110
00:07:25,680 --> 00:07:26,880
Let's talk about this

111
00:07:26,960 --> 00:07:28,200
when we get back.

112
00:07:28,680 --> 00:07:29,610
Have some water.

113
00:07:30,080 --> 00:07:30,440
Here.

114
00:07:42,200 --> 00:07:42,960
Guan Lin.

115
00:07:43,920 --> 00:07:45,920
You've been with me for these years,

116
00:07:46,480 --> 00:07:47,600
and I've only taught you

117
00:07:47,600 --> 00:07:49,600
this one skill.

118
00:07:53,159 --> 00:07:55,680
Don't complain it's too slow.

119
00:07:59,440 --> 00:08:00,320
Guan Lin.

120
00:08:01,760 --> 00:08:03,680
You need to know that firing a kiln

121
00:08:06,120 --> 00:08:07,480
is a lifelong pursuit.

122
00:08:09,200 --> 00:08:10,160
Master.

123
00:08:10,720 --> 00:08:11,920
I was wrong.

124
00:08:11,960 --> 00:08:12,320
I was

125
00:08:12,840 --> 00:08:13,960
too slow to realize.

126
00:08:13,960 --> 00:08:15,760
You should have told me this earlier.

127
00:08:15,760 --> 00:08:16,920
Actually, I was just anxious.

128
00:08:16,920 --> 00:08:18,250
I was worried about you.

129
00:08:20,280 --> 00:08:21,240
Don't cry.

130
00:08:21,240 --> 00:08:22,880
Why are you crying?

131
00:08:22,920 --> 00:08:23,980
No, I'm not crying.

132
00:08:25,960 --> 00:08:30,400
I'm still waiting to see what your first firing of Weijiayao

133
00:08:31,440 --> 00:08:32,760
will produce.

134
00:08:33,960 --> 00:08:35,799
I still want to see you

135
00:08:36,600 --> 00:08:37,880
become a master.

136
00:08:38,400 --> 00:08:40,240
And I'll become a grandmaster.

137
00:08:47,840 --> 00:08:50,560
Why are you wailing like we're in a soap opera?

138
00:08:54,800 --> 00:08:55,600
Students,

139
00:08:56,000 --> 00:08:57,000
time flies.

140
00:08:57,800 --> 00:08:58,560
In a flash,

141
00:08:59,080 --> 00:09:01,140
it's already the end of the semester.

142
00:09:01,320 --> 00:09:04,480
I won't take up too much of your time today.

143
00:09:05,080 --> 00:09:07,680
Xiaocen will collect your papers.

144
00:09:08,360 --> 00:09:09,720
Your final grades

145
00:09:10,080 --> 00:09:12,320
will be based on your papers

146
00:09:12,880 --> 00:09:15,240
and your regular assignments,

147
00:09:15,680 --> 00:09:17,280
which I will grade together.

148
00:09:18,200 --> 00:09:18,840
Students,

149
00:09:19,520 --> 00:09:22,120
you can check them after class.

150
00:09:27,880 --> 00:09:28,560
Xiaocen.

151
00:09:30,320 --> 00:09:32,120
How did you write your thesis?

152
00:09:34,760 --> 00:09:36,040
I wrote that

153
00:09:37,200 --> 00:09:38,530
porcelain restoration

154
00:09:38,760 --> 00:09:41,490
is actually a modern inheritance of ancient art.

155
00:09:41,960 --> 00:09:44,120
Inheritance means

156
00:09:44,760 --> 00:09:46,560
passing down the fundamentals,

157
00:09:47,080 --> 00:09:49,480
while adapting to current needs.

158
00:09:50,680 --> 00:09:52,920
Only by combining these two

159
00:09:53,400 --> 00:09:54,930
can it be true inheritance.

160
00:09:55,800 --> 00:09:58,360
This is also what I experienced

161
00:09:58,360 --> 00:09:59,960
and realized this semester.

162
00:10:01,520 --> 00:10:02,160
Xiaocen.

163
00:10:04,720 --> 00:10:06,760
You have a feel for art,

164
00:10:06,760 --> 00:10:08,920
and you are thoughtful and calm.

165
00:10:09,320 --> 00:10:11,840
These traits make you highly suited for

166
00:10:11,880 --> 00:10:13,610
cultural relics restoration.

167
00:10:14,400 --> 00:10:14,960
But,

168
00:10:16,560 --> 00:10:17,720
I heard your mother

169
00:10:18,680 --> 00:10:21,010
is arranging for you to change your major.

170
00:10:21,680 --> 00:10:22,720
What do you think?

171
00:10:27,560 --> 00:10:30,160
I think my family's opinion

172
00:10:30,160 --> 00:10:31,320
is quite important.

173
00:10:32,280 --> 00:10:33,880
I want to hear your opinion,

174
00:10:34,560 --> 00:10:35,640
your own thoughts.

175
00:10:38,040 --> 00:10:38,480
I...

176
00:10:39,000 --> 00:10:42,400
I seem to have always listened to my mother since I was little.

177
00:10:42,640 --> 00:10:43,360
Xiaocen.

178
00:10:44,080 --> 00:10:45,280
The first encounter.

179
00:10:46,120 --> 00:10:47,960
It all stems from fate.

180
00:10:49,760 --> 00:10:51,560
Only your own love

181
00:10:52,520 --> 00:10:54,760
can offset the long years.

182
00:10:57,920 --> 00:10:58,520
Of course,

183
00:10:58,800 --> 00:10:59,200
this

184
00:10:59,480 --> 00:11:02,000
also includes the people

185
00:11:02,880 --> 00:11:04,080
and things around us.

186
00:11:06,240 --> 00:11:07,240
Think about it.

187
00:11:09,520 --> 00:11:10,580
It's the holidays.

188
00:11:10,600 --> 00:11:12,600
I will read the paper when I get back.

189
00:11:12,800 --> 00:11:15,040
Think of your own answer.

190
00:11:16,520 --> 00:11:18,520
I believe you will find the answer.

191
00:11:19,200 --> 00:11:20,130
Happy holidays.

192
00:11:47,640 --> 00:11:48,700
It's so beautiful.

193
00:11:55,080 --> 00:11:56,200
The delicate shape

194
00:11:56,680 --> 00:11:57,680
and gentle luster

195
00:11:58,000 --> 00:11:59,930
complement each other perfectly.

196
00:12:03,080 --> 00:12:03,680
Master.

197
00:12:04,120 --> 00:12:04,800
Mr. Wei.

198
00:12:05,280 --> 00:12:05,920
It's done.

199
00:12:11,000 --> 00:12:11,400
Great.

200
00:12:11,480 --> 00:12:13,080
Congratulations, Mr. Guan.

201
00:12:13,080 --> 00:12:13,720
Next time,

202
00:12:14,000 --> 00:12:15,080
we must work with you again.

203
00:12:15,080 --> 00:12:15,640
Okay.

204
00:12:16,680 --> 00:12:17,210
Mr. Guan,

205
00:12:17,240 --> 00:12:18,640
can I take a photo with you?

206
00:12:18,640 --> 00:12:19,560
Sure. Come.

207
00:12:20,800 --> 00:12:21,280
Wait.

208
00:12:23,600 --> 00:12:24,320
Guan Lin.

209
00:12:26,320 --> 00:12:27,320
Come, sit here.

210
00:12:28,000 --> 00:12:28,960
It's inappropriate, Master.

211
00:12:28,960 --> 00:12:30,090
You should sit here.

212
00:12:31,760 --> 00:12:32,720
Sit down.

213
00:12:32,800 --> 00:12:33,200
No.

214
00:12:33,240 --> 00:12:34,040
Have a seat, Mr. Guan.

215
00:12:34,040 --> 00:12:34,840
Have a seat, Guan Lin.

216
00:12:34,840 --> 00:12:35,560
Sit down.

217
00:12:35,560 --> 00:12:36,080
Master, I...

218
00:12:36,080 --> 00:12:37,080
Take the picture.

219
00:12:39,400 --> 00:12:39,880
Please.

220
00:12:40,120 --> 00:12:41,720
Master, maybe you should...

221
00:12:41,800 --> 00:12:43,800
Don't look at me. Look at the camera.

222
00:12:44,680 --> 00:12:45,160
Three.

223
00:12:45,520 --> 00:12:46,000
Two.

224
00:12:46,480 --> 00:12:46,880
One.

225
00:12:47,320 --> 00:12:47,760
Smile.

226
00:13:11,840 --> 00:13:12,400
Sister,

227
00:13:13,480 --> 00:13:16,240
Xiaocen hasn't been eating well lately.

228
00:13:19,040 --> 00:13:19,900
It's a process.

229
00:13:20,640 --> 00:13:22,240
It'll be fine once it passes.

230
00:13:28,280 --> 00:13:29,320
As for her,

231
00:13:29,680 --> 00:13:31,340
she seems fine during the day.

232
00:13:32,640 --> 00:13:34,960
But at night, she often

233
00:13:35,120 --> 00:13:36,450
cries alone in her room.

234
00:13:37,600 --> 00:13:40,240
Sometimes I see her staring out the window.

235
00:13:43,280 --> 00:13:45,160
Xiaocen is already weak.

236
00:13:46,280 --> 00:13:48,680
She looks like the wind could blow her over.

237
00:13:49,240 --> 00:13:50,840
She's feeling so miserable,

238
00:13:51,360 --> 00:13:52,620
yet she won't tell you.

239
00:13:53,640 --> 00:13:55,200
It breaks my heart to see.

240
00:13:55,400 --> 00:13:57,000
It's because I care about her

241
00:13:57,040 --> 00:13:58,320
that I'm afraid she'll be wronged,

242
00:13:58,320 --> 00:14:00,180
with nowhere to cry in the future.

243
00:14:01,040 --> 00:14:02,680
Knowing it's impossible,

244
00:14:03,320 --> 00:14:04,720
why should I support her?

245
00:14:05,480 --> 00:14:07,480
Why are you so sure it won't work out?

246
00:14:08,920 --> 00:14:10,380
Let's make an assumption.

247
00:14:10,600 --> 00:14:11,720
I mean, what if.

248
00:14:13,560 --> 00:14:15,690
What if they actually end up together?

249
00:14:18,760 --> 00:14:20,720
Can't Xiaocen stay in Jingdezhen?

250
00:14:26,840 --> 00:14:29,280
It'd be good for her career here.

251
00:14:29,600 --> 00:14:30,600
Plus, I'm here too.

252
00:14:30,600 --> 00:14:31,680
I can help her.

253
00:14:34,720 --> 00:14:36,520
What if she stays in Jingdezhen?

254
00:14:39,680 --> 00:14:40,480
What if?

255
00:14:50,760 --> 00:14:52,620
What if she ends up like me? Right?

256
00:15:00,480 --> 00:15:01,160
Qingfang,

257
00:15:02,120 --> 00:15:04,200
can you stop dwelling on the past?

258
00:15:10,400 --> 00:15:11,080
If I don't,

259
00:15:12,240 --> 00:15:14,100
does that mean it never happened?

260
00:15:16,640 --> 00:15:17,400
Back then,

261
00:15:17,720 --> 00:15:19,780
you married and moved here all alone.

262
00:15:20,640 --> 00:15:21,570
Do you remember?

263
00:15:22,480 --> 00:15:24,210
You used to call me all the time.

264
00:15:24,840 --> 00:15:25,720
Qingfang,

265
00:15:26,360 --> 00:15:27,960
I'm not used to the food here.

266
00:15:27,960 --> 00:15:29,560
I can't adapt to the climate.

267
00:15:30,200 --> 00:15:31,080
And that man,

268
00:15:31,800 --> 00:15:33,060
didn't treat you well.

269
00:15:36,160 --> 00:15:36,960
Later,

270
00:15:38,200 --> 00:15:40,000
you raised Xing all by yourself.

271
00:15:40,720 --> 00:15:42,380
How did you get through it all?

272
00:15:43,520 --> 00:15:44,800
As your older sister,

273
00:15:45,800 --> 00:15:47,060
don't you think I know?

274
00:16:13,320 --> 00:16:13,880
Come in.

275
00:16:16,200 --> 00:16:16,720
Mom.

276
00:16:17,240 --> 00:16:17,840
Xiaocen.

277
00:16:18,120 --> 00:16:18,920
Well,

278
00:16:19,280 --> 00:16:21,800
you can pack up some things first

279
00:16:21,880 --> 00:16:22,680
and mail them.

280
00:16:22,720 --> 00:16:23,400
Got it.

281
00:16:24,560 --> 00:16:25,240
By the way,

282
00:16:25,480 --> 00:16:27,280
can you check your grades today?

283
00:16:30,240 --> 00:16:30,920
Okay.

284
00:16:31,400 --> 00:16:33,200
Take your time packing. No rush.

285
00:16:33,720 --> 00:16:34,920
I'll get back to work.

286
00:17:02,280 --> 00:17:03,720
Xu, what are you doing?

287
00:17:05,920 --> 00:17:06,920
Checking scores.

288
00:17:08,400 --> 00:17:09,400
Checking yours

289
00:17:09,400 --> 00:17:10,560
or Xiaocen's?

290
00:17:13,560 --> 00:17:14,920
You don't even know your own score,

291
00:17:14,920 --> 00:17:16,720
yet you're checking Xiaocen's?

292
00:17:18,000 --> 00:17:18,720
Okay, I won't ask.

293
00:17:18,720 --> 00:17:19,520
Just tell me,

294
00:17:19,520 --> 00:17:20,319
how did she do?

295
00:17:22,319 --> 00:17:23,079
Top five.

296
00:17:23,079 --> 00:17:23,800
Not bad!

297
00:17:23,880 --> 00:17:25,000
Such a big improvement.

298
00:17:25,000 --> 00:17:25,880
It must be you

299
00:17:25,880 --> 00:17:27,079
who tutored her well.

300
00:17:30,720 --> 00:17:32,240
Why don't you take the chance to call her?

301
00:17:32,240 --> 00:17:33,120
What are you waiting for?

302
00:17:33,120 --> 00:17:34,250
If you don't, I will.

303
00:17:34,800 --> 00:17:36,200
What's the number again?

304
00:17:37,800 --> 00:17:38,680
Just kidding.

305
00:17:38,880 --> 00:17:39,610
Call her now.

306
00:17:53,840 --> 00:17:54,600
Xiaocen.

307
00:17:55,360 --> 00:17:56,490
Initial encounters

308
00:17:57,360 --> 00:17:59,200
all stem from fate.

309
00:18:00,480 --> 00:18:02,200
Only your own passion

310
00:18:02,560 --> 00:18:04,880
can offset the long years.

311
00:18:05,280 --> 00:18:06,920
What exactly do I want?

312
00:18:16,200 --> 00:18:18,240
What exactly do I really want?

313
00:18:26,960 --> 00:18:27,480
Sister.

314
00:18:27,800 --> 00:18:29,680
These are some fruits for Xiaocen

315
00:18:29,720 --> 00:18:30,780
to eat on the plane.

316
00:18:31,560 --> 00:18:32,560
Oh, right. And...

317
00:18:34,040 --> 00:18:36,160
This is Jingdezhen porcelain for Brother-in-Law.

318
00:18:36,160 --> 00:18:37,320
There's also Fuliang tea inside.

319
00:18:37,320 --> 00:18:38,520
Okay, stop bringing things.

320
00:18:38,520 --> 00:18:39,720
It won't fit anymore.

321
00:18:40,320 --> 00:18:41,800
Isn't Brother-in-Law picking you up?

322
00:18:41,800 --> 00:18:42,930
You won't get tired.

323
00:18:44,720 --> 00:18:46,600
Cencen, get ready to go.

324
00:18:55,800 --> 00:18:56,280
Sister.

325
00:18:56,680 --> 00:18:58,920
Say hi to my brother-in-law for me when you get home.

326
00:18:58,920 --> 00:18:59,360
Okay.

327
00:19:00,480 --> 00:19:01,340
Let me tell you.

328
00:19:01,400 --> 00:19:02,880
You still need to discipline Xiaoxing,

329
00:19:02,880 --> 00:19:04,480
especially since he's a boy.

330
00:19:04,520 --> 00:19:05,720
You have to be strict

331
00:19:05,720 --> 00:19:06,720
and keep a close eye on him.

332
00:19:06,720 --> 00:19:07,560
Otherwise,

333
00:19:07,600 --> 00:19:08,400
he'll really get out of hand.

334
00:19:08,400 --> 00:19:08,960
Did you hear me?

335
00:19:08,960 --> 00:19:10,160
Don't worry, Sister.

336
00:19:10,520 --> 00:19:11,480
I got it.

337
00:19:11,720 --> 00:19:13,600
Remember to call me when you get home.

338
00:19:13,600 --> 00:19:15,730
You should think more about yourself.

339
00:19:15,800 --> 00:19:16,920
Follow your heart.

340
00:19:17,360 --> 00:19:19,090
No matter what choice you make,

341
00:19:19,760 --> 00:19:20,560
I will respect

342
00:19:22,200 --> 00:19:23,130
and support you.

343
00:19:24,720 --> 00:19:25,800
Xiaocen, hurry up.

344
00:19:27,520 --> 00:19:28,580
Mom, I'm not going.

345
00:19:33,240 --> 00:19:34,170
What did you say?

346
00:19:35,800 --> 00:19:36,200
I...

347
00:19:36,600 --> 00:19:37,860
I said I'm not leaving.

348
00:19:40,480 --> 00:19:41,840
No, what do you mean?

349
00:19:42,200 --> 00:19:43,200
Aren't you going back to

350
00:19:43,200 --> 00:19:45,130
keep your dad company this summer?

351
00:19:45,720 --> 00:19:47,040
I already told Dad.

352
00:19:47,640 --> 00:19:49,970
I'm staying at my aunt's for the holidays.

353
00:19:52,240 --> 00:19:53,680
What I want to tell you is,

354
00:19:56,360 --> 00:19:58,360
I'm not leaving afterwards either.

355
00:20:00,520 --> 00:20:02,580
What nonsense are you talking about?

356
00:20:04,080 --> 00:20:06,120
Go through security with me right now.

357
00:20:06,120 --> 00:20:07,520
We can talk when we get home.

358
00:20:07,520 --> 00:20:09,650
I need to make it clear to you right now.

359
00:20:10,120 --> 00:20:11,480
I'm not leaving today.

360
00:20:13,840 --> 00:20:15,120
Did that guy named Xu Xiao

361
00:20:15,120 --> 00:20:16,880
tell you a bunch of nonsense?

362
00:20:16,880 --> 00:20:17,440
No.

363
00:20:18,800 --> 00:20:20,260
These are my own thoughts.

364
00:20:23,320 --> 00:20:23,800
Mom.

365
00:20:24,720 --> 00:20:26,600
I'm 19 years old now.

366
00:20:27,720 --> 00:20:29,850
I have the right to make my own choices.

367
00:20:31,560 --> 00:20:33,920
I've always listened to you since I was little.

368
00:20:33,920 --> 00:20:34,720
You said

369
00:20:35,360 --> 00:20:37,560
eating too much sugar is bad for health,

370
00:20:38,720 --> 00:20:40,080
so I barely ate any.

371
00:20:41,480 --> 00:20:43,940
You said girls shouldn't dress too flashily

372
00:20:44,000 --> 00:20:45,360
or wear heavy makeup.

373
00:20:45,520 --> 00:20:47,080
You also said Chinese medicine should be drunk in one gulp.

374
00:20:47,080 --> 00:20:48,340
I listened to all of it.

375
00:20:49,120 --> 00:20:51,040
Because I know you mean well.

376
00:20:52,840 --> 00:20:54,320
But gradually, I can't tell

377
00:20:54,320 --> 00:20:55,240
which are your thoughts

378
00:20:55,240 --> 00:20:56,560
and which are my own.

379
00:20:58,720 --> 00:20:59,240
Mom.

380
00:21:00,280 --> 00:21:03,010
You were the one who told me to come to Jingdezhen.

381
00:21:03,080 --> 00:21:05,810
You made me choose cultural relics restoration.

382
00:21:07,560 --> 00:21:09,280
Before I came here, I didn't know

383
00:21:09,280 --> 00:21:10,610
what I would go through.

384
00:21:12,680 --> 00:21:13,880
But I found that

385
00:21:14,840 --> 00:21:16,600
I fell in love with porcelain

386
00:21:23,280 --> 00:21:24,680
and cultural relics.

387
00:21:32,040 --> 00:21:33,770
I fell in love with Jingdezhen.

388
00:21:45,960 --> 00:21:47,420
I fell in love with Xu Xiao.

389
00:21:52,880 --> 00:21:53,720
I found that

390
00:21:53,720 --> 00:21:55,040
when I do things,

391
00:21:55,040 --> 00:21:56,480
I can have emotions.

392
00:21:57,640 --> 00:21:58,680
I can be happy,

393
00:21:58,680 --> 00:21:59,360
cheerful,

394
00:21:59,360 --> 00:22:01,560
and find it hard to let go of some things.

395
00:22:04,040 --> 00:22:05,640
I don't have to listen to you.

396
00:22:11,560 --> 00:22:13,480
I fell in love with cultural relics restoration.

397
00:22:13,480 --> 00:22:16,540
Four years of college is not enough for me to explore it.

398
00:22:16,840 --> 00:22:17,840
I want to stay here

399
00:22:18,560 --> 00:22:21,220
and spend my whole life exploring and learning.

400
00:22:23,120 --> 00:22:24,050
Your whole life?

401
00:22:25,600 --> 00:22:26,880
How old are you now

402
00:22:27,640 --> 00:22:29,640
to be talking about your whole life?

403
00:22:30,240 --> 00:22:30,920
All I know is

404
00:22:30,920 --> 00:22:33,780
that this is the first time I have a clear direction.

405
00:22:34,040 --> 00:22:36,040
Nothing you say will change my mind.

406
00:22:39,600 --> 00:22:40,320
Right now,

407
00:22:40,920 --> 00:22:42,960
I don't want to discuss this with you anymore.

408
00:22:42,960 --> 00:22:44,120
Right now, immediately,

409
00:22:44,120 --> 00:22:45,850
come through security with me.

410
00:22:47,320 --> 00:22:47,880
Aunt.

411
00:22:49,240 --> 00:22:50,500
I'll go to your car now.

412
00:22:53,600 --> 00:22:54,400
Zhao Xiaocen!

413
00:22:55,600 --> 00:22:56,400
Zhao Xiaocen!

414
00:22:57,920 --> 00:22:59,580
The car is unlocked, Xiaocen!

415
00:23:25,400 --> 00:23:26,000
Qingfang.

416
00:23:27,040 --> 00:23:28,170
Since we were young,

417
00:23:28,840 --> 00:23:29,920
you were 90% right

418
00:23:30,400 --> 00:23:31,920
about everything.

419
00:23:33,280 --> 00:23:34,560
But today,

420
00:23:34,840 --> 00:23:36,900
I don't think you did the right thing.

421
00:23:38,520 --> 00:23:40,600
Did you hear what Xiaocen just said?

422
00:23:42,280 --> 00:23:43,360
For all these years,

423
00:23:43,360 --> 00:23:44,360
this is the first time

424
00:23:44,360 --> 00:23:45,400
I've seen her so determined

425
00:23:45,400 --> 00:23:46,720
to do something.

426
00:23:51,600 --> 00:23:52,120
Yes.

427
00:23:54,040 --> 00:23:56,370
Looking at the way she spoke to me just now,

428
00:23:57,720 --> 00:24:00,120
I almost didn't recognize my own daughter.

429
00:24:02,240 --> 00:24:04,400
Look whose daughter she is.

430
00:24:08,040 --> 00:24:09,720
I'm just afraid she'll regret it later,

431
00:24:09,720 --> 00:24:10,680
you know?

432
00:24:11,160 --> 00:24:13,220
You always say we'll regret it later.

433
00:24:14,720 --> 00:24:15,720
But you know what?

434
00:24:16,480 --> 00:24:17,610
For all these years,

435
00:24:17,840 --> 00:24:18,840
there's something

436
00:24:18,840 --> 00:24:20,320
I never dared to tell you.

437
00:24:24,120 --> 00:24:25,580
I have never regretted it.

438
00:24:27,360 --> 00:24:29,120
You can say I chose the wrong man,

439
00:24:29,120 --> 00:24:31,320
but I have never regretted coming here.

440
00:24:32,840 --> 00:24:34,640
If I hadn't come to Jingdezhen,

441
00:24:35,200 --> 00:24:36,930
I wouldn't have my current life

442
00:24:37,480 --> 00:24:38,400
and career,

443
00:24:39,200 --> 00:24:40,600
let alone Xing.

444
00:24:41,720 --> 00:24:43,120
I love everything here.

445
00:24:47,880 --> 00:24:48,480
Qingfang,

446
00:24:49,600 --> 00:24:51,460
give yourself a little more time,

447
00:24:51,800 --> 00:24:53,840
and you will fall in love with this place

448
00:24:53,840 --> 00:24:55,240
just like Xiaocen and me.

449
00:25:39,160 --> 00:25:39,920
Mom.

450
00:25:41,640 --> 00:25:42,160
Sister.

451
00:25:43,560 --> 00:25:44,040
Sister.

452
00:25:54,000 --> 00:25:54,640
Mom.

453
00:26:09,280 --> 00:26:10,200
Cencen.

454
00:26:11,840 --> 00:26:12,400
Cencen.

455
00:26:24,920 --> 00:26:26,960
Let's all calm down for a bit.

456
00:26:29,920 --> 00:26:31,120
I'll head back first.

457
00:26:37,280 --> 00:26:38,040
It seems

458
00:26:39,080 --> 00:26:40,720
I really should accept

459
00:26:41,720 --> 00:26:43,120
that you've grown up.

460
00:26:46,960 --> 00:26:47,690
Stop crying.

461
00:26:52,120 --> 00:26:53,240
Thank you, Mom.

462
00:26:53,240 --> 00:26:53,680
Don't cry.
